{"tid":2050294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"萬人被捕 撐傘擋椒如港抗爭","createTime":"2020-06-04T04:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T04:45:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"528f0925aaf7c60a3bcede0191ef8ffe7e735df4","tid":2050294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200604/SCRU5RR73KL7SXONMFEEKDUMQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2FSCRU5RR73KL7SXONMFEEKDUMQA%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=ee68b8a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2FSCRU5RR73KL7SXONMFEEKDUMQA%2F&h=c4a12c0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200604/SCRU5RR73KL7SXONMFEEKDUMQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n萬人被捕 撐傘擋椒如港抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N2L6AAMMVQOSLA3KBSD4F6V2XM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN2L6AAMMVQOSLA3KBSD4F6V2XM.jpg&h=70981796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【西雅圖】示威者撐傘擋椒令CNN記者想起香港。 <br />\n<br />\n黑人弗洛伊德死於警暴觸發的示威持續八日，據報全美逾1.1萬人被捕，但民眾仍繼續堅持上街，有首次示威的少女稱不想再沉默。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：軍方憂淪政治打手損害威信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首次示威少女︰不想再沉默<br />\n<br />\n網媒BuzzFeed前日引述30地警察部門的數字報道，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「他向我表達感受的方式，和他覺得要押上性命上街令我心碎」，於是她也決定冒險，但軍方介入令她不敢再上街。<br />\n<br />\n美國多間傳媒。。。。。。。。。但暴力行為大大減少。<br />\n<br />\n然而，波特蘭和西雅圖亦有警察以武力驅散人群，前晚在西雅圖市議會一帶聚集、站在警方防線前的數百名示威者中，前線不乏撐起雨傘遮擋警方鎮暴武器如胡椒噴霧的人，有線新聞網絡（CNN）記者指畫面讓人想起去年的香港反送中示威。<br />\n路透社"}]}